{"tid":2421340,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【股票印花稅】港加印花稅　美國證監調低賣出美股收費七成","createTime":"2021-02-24T12:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T12:48:16.000Z","uid":352873,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"adf4393ec232493930a5c4106d7519f9387e705a","tid":2421340,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:27:19.000Z","msg":"環球證券交易所下調交易徵費是大趨勢，港府卻決定調高股票印花稅，觸發港交所 （00388） 以致整個港股市場急挫。巧合的是，香港調高買賣港股收費的同一天，美國卻宣布減股票交易徵費。美國證券交易委員會（SEC）公告，自2月25日起，美國證監會的賣出股票收費標準，將由0.00221%降至0.00051%。<br />\n<br />\n渣打銀行公布，將自25日起，將賣出美股收費，由0.00221%降至0.00051%。至於券商冠力金融稱，所有於2月18日或之後結算的美股交易，賣出美股收費，將由0.00207%降至0.00221%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2885706/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E6%8B%93%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%91%E5%82%B3%E7%91%9E%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%8A%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80%E5%B0%87%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%94%B1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%B7%E5%BE%80%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%80%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2?mtc=20031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2885706%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%258B%2593%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2591%259E%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%2591%259E%25E9%258A%2580%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%2594%25B1%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2581%25B7%25E5%25BE%2580%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%258B%25A2%3Fmtc%3D20031&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8DH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=1d91b7ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2885706/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E6%8B%93%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%91%E5%82%B3%E7%91%9E%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%8A%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80%E5%B0%87%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%94%B1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%B7%E5%BE%80%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%80%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%84%A